@baseUrl = https://form-api.kidrawer.com/v1
@tenantId = ten_demo
@jwt = REPLACE_WITH_COGNITO_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Org profile (tenant resolved from JWT claim)
GET {{baseUrl}}/org/me
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Org courses list (no tenant header required in cognito mode)
GET {{baseUrl}}/org/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Org courses list with matching tenant header (optional)
GET {{baseUrl}}/org/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

### Tenant mismatch check (expect 403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/org/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
x-tenant-id: ten_other

### Tenant route mismatch check (expect 403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/org/tenants/ten_other/check
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
